snippet.title: ONE PIECE World Seeker – Opening Cutscene
snippet.description:
Luffy and the Straw Hat Pirates find themselves on an exciting new adventure on Prison Island. See how it all begins in this opening cutscene from One Piece World Seeker!

On March 15th, set sail on your journey in One Piece World Seeker! Pre-Order Today: bandainam.co/ONEPIECE
